{"tid":315703,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"創意爸帶女玩人力過山車 迪士尼都唔及佢咁正","createTime":"2017-07-10T08:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T08:18:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"250fbfb8a64d30793c77db711f30c9f7502aa1c6","tid":315703,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:09:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170710/20084872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170710%2F20084872&d=MztyRjsAgva3HKh98OarSjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=06ea33f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170710%2F20084872&h=8571ee1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170710/20084872</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n創意爸帶女玩人力過山車<br />\n迪士尼都唔及佢咁正<br />\n<br />\n快樂不一定要用錢買！美國一名2歲女童想到迪士尼樂園玩，父親雖負擔不來高昂的入場費，但為了滿足愛女，他想出「手動過山車」的創意點子，把迪士尼過山車「帶回」家中。<br />\n<br />\n父親皮諾（Victor Peoro）為了女兒奧特姆（Autumn）炮製了這個窩心的「手動遊戲」。他讓女兒坐進一個塑膠箱裏權充過山車車廂，在大電視上播放第一身視角的過山車片段，然後他雙手舉起膠箱站在電視機前，配合著畫面擺弄膠箱，模擬玩過山車的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n看著過山車的畫面，皮諾跟女兒說「我們玩過山車了」，然後按著畫面左右、上下搖動膠箱，當畫面上過山車「爬高」時皮諾也讓女兒往上傾斜，向下急衝時，女兒的箱子也微微朝下，模擬的效果看來相當不錯，因為小女孩一直咭咭笑，女兒開心皮諾當然也開心，兩父女露出燦爛的笑容。<br />\n<br />\n「我女兒想去迪士尼樂園，但實在太昂貴，我們有另類玩法。」皮諾把片段上載到YouTube，題為「窮人過山車」，大受網民讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》／美國霍士新聞  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n燃料高度易燃　金仔洲際導彈旁吸煙唔識死？<br />\n下一則<br />\n與世隔絕18年　一家三口住深山自給自足<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e047865cec3e34bb546c45b31441190dc21c38fb","tid":315703,"uid":22424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"窮人學人生仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d30a88596b76402e680a27535ca38e38f3500bb","tid":315703,"uid":86893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮人學人生仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個女囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}